															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610164528" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;" >psul</a></span> <span class="odate time_1491895979 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">11 Apr 2017 07:32</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2789271">
									

<p>This was inspired by the 3000 contest. This does not qualify for the contest for a number of reasons.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-645903-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-645903-1')">1</a></sup> This is just a tribute to the fact that horror can exist without the need for the anomalous.</p>
<p>Many thanks to sirpudding, shaggydredlocks, Don1Charles and Petrograd (and anyone else I've missed) for their thoughts and feedback. Much appreciated, as always.</p>
<div class="footnotes-footer">
<div class="title">Footnotes</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-645903-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-645903-1')">1</a>. Not least the fact that <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/3000contestpsul">I have already entered</a></div>
</div>

