			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2789351">
									

<p>I really like the idea of 3000 being an -EX, even though it won't be. But is this truly Explained? It looks like an ambiguous case - maybe anomalous, maybe not, insufficient evidence either way.</p>
<p>Definitely worth reposting as a non-3000, either way.</p>
<p>Also, is there a &quot;not&quot; missing here in this sentence?</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Officer Douglas was adamant that he had nothing to hide, but admitted that he could rule out tampering with the crime scene or the evidence during the alleged gaps.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>&quot;he could <strong>not</strong> rule out?&quot;</p>

