			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2789696">
									

<p>These agents have to have been read into <em>something</em> to have need to know and a file has to be started under <em>some codename</em> to get started on collecting information. Now it is possible that the Foundation starts with a codename other than an SCP designation and then changes it later once they instate containment procedures, but it is also possible they start with the SCP designation as a provisional codename in the first place. If the majority of objects collected by the Foundation do end up with SCPs for some length of time then it makes sense to simplify the process and do the latter.</p>

							</div>

								
